er":23,"title":"v1.21.0","description":"","creator":{"login":"caarlos0","id":245435,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NTQzNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/245435?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0","html_url":"https://github.com/caarlos0","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":58,"state":"closed","created_at":"2023-08-12T17:18:17Z","updated_at":"2023-09-23T03:50:30Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":"2023-09-23T03:43:18Z"},"comments":1,"created_at":"2023-08-14T14:47:57Z","updated_at":"2023-08-15T13:24:55Z","closed_at":"2023-08-15T13:24:54Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### What happened?\n\nWhen running a snapshot build, the version passed as `{{ .Version }}` to the global hooks differs from the one specified in `snapshot.name_template`.\r\n\r\nThis is due to the snapshot pipe running after the before pipe (https://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/blob/4526c5b6813ade905f9658467c3a85aa25bdc9b9/internal/pipeline/pipeline.go#L62-L65), thus the global hooks receive the semver parsed version off the tag, yet not the modified version.\r\n\r\nOnce one builds a binary with ldflags and passes the version to a variable in the binary, the versions are different.\r\n\r\nThis can be especially hard to deal with when the before hooks generate version-specific files embedded into the binary.\n\n### How can we reproduce this?\n\nI've created a small repo for this showcase: https://github.com/ThomasK33/goreleaser-snapshot-precedence-repro\n\n### goreleaser version\n\n```bash\n‚ùØ goreleaser --version\r\n  ____       ____      _\r\n / ___| ___ |  _ \\ ___| | ___  __ _ ___  ___ _ __\r\n| |  _ / _ \\| |_) / _ \\ |/ _ \\/ _` / __|/ _ \\ '__|\r\n| |_| | (_) |  _ <  __/ |  __/ (_| \\__ \\  __/ |\r\n \\____|\\___/|_| \\_\\___|_|\\___|\\__,_|___/\\___|_|\r\ngoreleaser: Deliver Go Binaries as fast and easily as possible\r\nhttps://goreleaser.com\r\n\r\nGitVersion:    1.20.0\r\nGitCommit:     56c9d09a1b925e2549631c6d180b0a1c2ebfac82\r\nGitTreeState:  false\r\nBuildDate:     2023-08-10T01:23:44Z\r\nBuiltBy:       goreleaser\r\nGoVersion:     go1.21.0\r\nCompiler:      gc\r\nModuleSum:     h1:wvAbDqQwMX3PWPYc4VIeaWQB2V5HOETvDlyfTrk7NgQ=\r\nPlatform:      darwin/arm64\n```\n\n\n### GoReleaser Check\n\n- [X] goreleaser check shows no errors\n\n### Search\n\n- [X] I did search for other open and closed issues before opening this\n\n### Supporter\n\n- [ ] I am a [sponsor](https://github.com/sponsors/caarlos0/) or a [Pro](https://goreleaser.com/pro) customer\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct\n\n### Additional context\n\nI think this can be fixed by changing\r\n\r\n```go\r\n    // run global hooks before build\r\n    before.Pipe{},\r\n    // snapshot version handling\r\n    snapshot.Pipe{},\r\n```\r\n\r\nto \r\n\r\n```go\r\n    // snapshot version handling\r\n    snapshot.Pipe{},\r\n    // run global hooks before build\r\n    before.Pipe{},\r\n```\r\n\r\nin the [internal/pipeline/pipeline.go](https://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/blob/4526c5b6813ade905f9658467c3a85aa25bdc9b9/internal/pipeline/pipeline.go#L62-L65) file.\r\n\r\nIf that's fine by you, I'd be more than happy to open a PR with that change.","closed_by":{"login":"caarlos0","id":245435,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NTQzNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/245435?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0","html_url":"https://github.com/caarlos0","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/4247/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/4247/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}